"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"The US president says Iran has agreed to turn over its enriched uranium, but Tehran has not commented on the claim. This is a significant development in international relations, as it could impact the ongoing tensions between the US and Iran.\",            \"english_title\": \"US-Iran Uranium Agreement\",            \"translated_version\": \"El presidente de EE.UU. dice que Ir\u00e1n ha aceptado entregar su uranio enriquecido, pero Teher\u00e1n no ha comentado sobre esto. Esto es importante para las relaciones internacionales, porque puede afectar las tensiones entre EE.UU. e Ir\u00e1n.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Acuerdo de Uranio EE.UU.-Ir\u00e1n\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Few Israelis see this truce as a way out of the conflict with Hezbollah, the BBC's Lucy Williamson writes. The situation remains tense, and many are skeptical about the effectiveness of the truce in bringing lasting peace.\",            \"english_title\": \"Truce with Hezbollah\",            \"translated_version\": \"Pocos israel\u00edes ven esta tregua como una soluci\u00f3n al conflicto con Hezbollah, escribe Lucy Williamson de la BBC. La situaci\u00f3n sigue tensa y muchos dudan de que la tregua traiga paz duradera.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Tregua con Hezbollah\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The remains of 14-year-old Celeste Rivas Hernandez were found in the singer's car last year. This discovery has raised many questions and concerns about the circumstances surrounding her death.\",            \"english_title\": \"Discovery of Celeste's Remains\",            \"translated_version\": \"Los restos de Celeste Rivas Hernandez, de 14 a\u00f1os, fueron encontrados en el coche del cantante el a\u00f1o pasado. Este descubrimiento ha generado muchas preguntas y preocupaciones sobre su muerte.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Descubrimiento de Restos de Celeste\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Experts say Mythos potentially has an unprecedented ability to identify and exploit cyber-security weaknesses. This could have major implications for global cyber-security, as it highlights the need for improved defenses against such threats.\",            \"english_title\": \"Mythos and Cyber-Security\",            \"translated_version\": \"Los expertos dicen que Mythos tiene una habilidad \u00fanica para encontrar y usar debilidades en la ciberseguridad. Esto puede tener grandes efectos en la ciberseguridad mundial, mostrando la necesidad de mejores defensas.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Mythos y Ciberseguridad\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"At least 16 people were injured in a shooting at a high school on Tuesday, before another nine were killed in a separate school shooting on Wednesday. These tragic events have sparked renewed debates about gun control and safety in schools.\",            \"english_title\": \"School Shootings Tragedy\",            \"translated_version\": \"Al menos 16 personas resultaron heridas en un tiroteo en una escuela secundaria el martes, y otras nueve murieron en otro tiroteo escolar el mi\u00e9rcoles. Estos eventos tr\u00e1gicos han iniciado nuevos debates sobre el control de armas y la seguridad en las escuelas.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Tragedia de Tiroteos Escolares\"        }    ]}"